<div class="tlp-pane-container">
    <section class="tlp-pane-section">
        <p>{{# dgettext }}tuleap-program_management | Aggregate others projects to have an overall view of your Program activities. These projects will be considered as Teams.{{/ dgettext }}</p>
        <p>{{# dgettext }}tuleap-program_management | Good to know:{{/ dgettext }}</p>
        <ul>
            <li>{{# dgettext }}tuleap-program_management | You must be administrator of the projects you want aggregate.{{/ dgettext }}</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="tlp-form-element tlp-form-element-append program-management-form-choose-teams">
            <select class="tlp-select" id="program-management-choose-teams" name="list-value">
                <option value=""></option>
                {{# potential_teams }}
                    <option value="{{ id }}"><span aria-hidden="true">{{project_icon}}</span> {{ public_name }}</option>
                {{/ potential_teams }}
            </select>
            <button type="button" class="tlp-append tlp-button tlp-button-primary" id="program-management-add-team-button" data-test="program-management-add-team-button">
                <i class="fas fa-plus tlp-button-icon" aria-hidden="true"></i>{{# dgettext }}tuleap-program_management | Aggregate project{{/ dgettext }}
            </button>
        </div>
        <div class="tlp-alert-danger program-management-error-rest-not-show" id="program-management-add-team-error-rest"></div>
    </section>
</div>
